<local:MyCard Title="获取资源包" Margin="0,0,0,15">
    <StackPanel Margin="25,40,23,15">
        <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" Margin="0,0,0,4"
                   Text="你可以在许多相关资源网站找到资源包，诸如 CurseForge、Modrinth。你可以点击下面的按钮来快速跳转至这些网站：" />
        <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal" HorizontalAlignment="Left">
            <local:MyButton Margin="0,4,20,0" Height="35" HorizontalAlignment="Left" Padding="13,0,13,0"
                        Text="CurseForge 资源包下载" EventType="打开网页" EventData="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/search?class=texture-packs" />
            <local:MyButton Margin="0,4,20,0" Height="35" HorizontalAlignment="Left" Padding="13,0,13,0"
                        Text="Modrinth 资源包下载" EventType="打开网页" EventData="https://modrinth.com/resourcepacks" />
        </StackPanel>
        <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" Margin="0,8,0,4"
                   Text="同时，PCL 中也提供了资源包的下载渠道，你可以在 “下载 → 资源包” 中找到你所需的资源包。" />
    </StackPanel>
</local:MyCard>

<local:MyCard Title="导入纹理包（材质包）" Margin="0,0,0,15">
    <StackPanel Margin="25,40,23,15">
        <Grid>
            <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" Margin="0,15,0,4" Width="200"
                        Text="1. 选择您想要安装资源包的版本后，点击 “版本设置”。" HorizontalAlignment="Left" />
            <local:MyImage Margin="250,0,0,0" HorizontalAlignment="Center" Source="https://i1.hdslb.com/bfs/article/98bb710db3f3fd90954ece31bd22fd45565437509.jpg" />
        </Grid>

        <Grid Margin="0,20,0,4">
            <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" Margin="0,15,0,4" Width="200"
                        Text="2. 于 “快捷方式” 一栏中点击 “存档文件夹” 按钮。" HorizontalAlignment="Left" />
            <local:MyImage Margin="250,0,0,0" HorizontalAlignment="Center" Source="https://i1.hdslb.com/bfs/article/dd4475d0af0c5cb13ec9eff147c01370565437509.png" />
        </Grid>

        <Grid Margin="0,20,0,4">
            <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" Margin="0,15,0,4" Width="200"
                        Text="3. 此时，您应该能在弹出的资源管理器界面中看见 “resourcepacks” 文件夹。" HorizontalAlignment="Left" />
            <local:MyImage Margin="250,0,0,0" HorizontalAlignment="Center" Source="https://i1.hdslb.com/bfs/article/2008241d50dc698e0c4270fe3042fefb565437509.png" />
        </Grid>

        <Grid Margin="0,20,0,4">
            <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" Margin="0,15,0,4" Width="200"
                        Text="4. 打开 “resourcepacks” 文件夹，并将您的资源包拖入 “resourcepacks” 文件夹。" HorizontalAlignment="Left" />
            <local:MyImage Margin="250,0,0,0" HorizontalAlignment="Center" Source="https://i1.hdslb.com/bfs/article/30dc1117fdbeb9f520da36fa99c9f30a565437509.png" />
        </Grid>
        <local:MyHint Margin="0,15,0,0" Text="部分资源包压缩包主体内套入了一个文件夹，此时你可以直接将此文件夹解压至 “resourcepacks” 文件夹使用。" IsWarn="False" />
        <local:MyImage HorizontalAlignment="Center" Margin="50,15,50,0" Source="https://i1.hdslb.com/bfs/article/9253fc094f2defd2419839d3464c1231565437509.png"/>
        <local:MyImage HorizontalAlignment="Center" Margin="50,15,50,0" Source="https://i1.hdslb.com/bfs/article/874d24aacf6ce16e6429f347d6dff50b565437509.png"/>
    </StackPanel>
</local:MyCard>

<local:MyCard Title="启用纹理包（材质包）" Margin="0,0,0,15">
    <StackPanel Margin="25,40,23,15">
        <Grid>
            <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" Margin="0,15,0,4" Width="200"
                        Text="1. 启动游戏，打开 “选项” → “资源包”。" HorizontalAlignment="Left" />
                <StackPanel Margin="250,0,0,0">
                    <local:MyImage HorizontalAlignment="Center" Source="https://i1.hdslb.com/bfs/article/785dcb74a2f8f54d76d68146a055b889565437509.jpg" />
                    <local:MyImage HorizontalAlignment="Center" Margin="0,15,0,0" Source="https://i1.hdslb.com/bfs/new_dyn/00ad128a8eb41d45355aa189d7e747d4558830935.png@.webp" />
                </StackPanel>
        </Grid>

        <Grid Margin="0,20,0,4">
            <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" Margin="0,15,0,4" Width="200"
                        Text="2. 此时，左侧 “可用” 列表中罗列有尚未启用的资源包。将鼠标指针移动至资源包图标上方，点击出现的箭头，使该资源包将移动至右侧 “已选” 列表后，点击 “完成” 后即可应用资源包。" HorizontalAlignment="Left" />
            <StackPanel Margin="250,0,0,0">
                <local:MyImage HorizontalAlignment="Center" Source="https://i1.hdslb.com/bfs/article/1ed178070384d06b65edf3a608ca0886565437509.png" />
                <local:MyImage HorizontalAlignment="Center" Margin="0,15,0,0" Source="https://i1.hdslb.com/bfs/article/a24ba1dbbdf80f7be9fb77f15054453f565437509.png" />
            </StackPanel>
        </Grid>
    </StackPanel>
</local:MyCard>

<local:MyCard Title="对于 1.16 以上版本的安装方法" Margin="0,0,0,15" CanSwap="True" IsSwapped="True">
    <StackPanel Margin="25,40,23,15">
        <local:MyHint Text="这是 1.16 以上版本的更快捷的安装方式，你依旧可以使用上面的方式来安装材质。" IsWarn="False" />

        <Grid Margin="0,20,0,4">
            <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" Margin="0,15,0,4" Width="200"
                        Text="1. 启动游戏，打开 “选项” → “资源包”。" HorizontalAlignment="Left" />
                <StackPanel Margin="250,0,0,0">
                  <local:MyImage HorizontalAlignment="Center" Source="https://i1.hdslb.com/bfs/article/785dcb74a2f8f54d76d68146a055b889565437509.jpg" />
                  <local:MyImage HorizontalAlignment="Center" Margin="0,15,0,0" Source="https://i1.hdslb.com/bfs/new_dyn/00ad128a8eb41d45355aa189d7e747d4558830935.png@.webp" />
                </StackPanel>
        </Grid>

        <Grid Margin="0,20,0,4">
            <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" Margin="0,15,0,4" Width="200"
                        Text="2. 将您的资源包文件直接拖至 Minecraft 窗口内。此时会弹出一个提示询问安装，点击 “是”。" HorizontalAlignment="Left" />
            <local:MyImage Margin="250,0,0,0" HorizontalAlignment="Center" Source="https://i1.hdslb.com/bfs/new_dyn/efb6f458f93b86846e9ac04f1c920c5b558830935.png@.webp" />
        </Grid>

        <Grid Margin="0,20,0,4">
            <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" Margin="0,15,0,4" Width="200"
                        Text="3. 此时，左侧 “可用” 列表中罗列有尚未启用的资源包。将鼠标指针移动至资源包图标上方，点击出现的箭头，使该资源包将移动至右侧 “已选” 列表后，点击 “完成” 后即可应用资源包。" HorizontalAlignment="Left" />
            <StackPanel Margin="250,0,0,0">
                <local:MyImage HorizontalAlignment="Center" Source="https://i1.hdslb.com/bfs/article/1ed178070384d06b65edf3a608ca0886565437509.png" />
                <local:MyImage HorizontalAlignment="Center" Margin="0,15,0,0" Source="https://i1.hdslb.com/bfs/article/a24ba1dbbdf80f7be9fb77f15054453f565437509.png" />
            </StackPanel>
        </Grid>
    </StackPanel>
</local:MyCard>
